(A–B) 
<taxonomicName id="88844D345356FF98FF6E8283FD3CF836" authority=", MNHN IE." authorityName="MNHN IE." box="[346,660,1920,1944]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiuridae" genus="Ophiura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="ljungmani">
<emphasis id="7DF0EAA55356FF98FF6E8283FDB4F836" box="[346,540,1920,1944]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Ophiura ljungmani</emphasis>
, MNHN IE.
</taxonomicName>
2009.1623, A: dorsal and B: ventral views. (C–E) 
<taxonomicName id="88844D345356FF98FAB68283FF1CF812" authority=", MNHN IE." authorityName="MNHN IE." class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiuridae" genus="Ophiura" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="trimeni">
<emphasis id="7DF0EAA55356FF98FAB68283FB70F836" box="[1154,1240,1920,1944]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Ophiura</emphasis>
cf. 
<emphasis id="7DF0EAA55356FF98FACF8282FAECF836" box="[1275,1348,1921,1944]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">trimeni</emphasis>
, MNHN IE.
</taxonomicName>
2009.1620, C: dorsal outline, D: dorsal and E: ventral views. (F–H) 
<taxonomicName id="88844D345356FF98FD4382A7FB86F812" box="[887,1070,1956,1980]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiopyrgidae" genus="Ophioplinthus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="undetermined">
